<body>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="effective-date">Effective Date: February 20, 2025</p>

    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>Welcome to ChoiceBot. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring a safe user experience. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our app.</p>

    <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <h3>a. Personal Information</h3>
    <p>We collect the following personal information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Email Address: For account creation and authentication</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>b. Usage Data</h3>
    <p>We collect data on how you interact with the app, including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Features accessed</li>
        <li>Time spent on the app</li>
        <li>Interaction patterns</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>c. Device Information</h3>
    <p>We collect information about your device, such as:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Device model</li>
        <li>Operating system version</li>
        <li>Unique device identifiers</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide and improve app functionality</li>
        <li>Authenticate users</li>
        <li>Personalize user experience</li>
        <li>Communicate updates and respond to inquiries</li>
        <li>Enhance app security</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
    <p>Your data is securely stored in Firebase. We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.</p>

    <h2>5. Sharing of Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information with third-party service providers who assist in app operations, provided they adhere to strict data protection standards.</p>

    <h2>6. User Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Request corrections</li>
        <li>Delete your account</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent for data processing</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise these rights, contact us through the app's support feature.</p>

    <h2>7. Biometric Data</h2>
    <p>ChoiceBot offers biometric login (Face ID/Touch ID) for enhanced security. Biometric data is stored securely on your device and is not transmitted to our servers.</p>

    <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>ChoiceBot is not intended for users under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware of such data, we will take steps to delete it promptly.</p>

    <h2>9. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy within the app. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.</p>

    <h2>10. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at choicebott@gmail.com</p>
